P^{(2)}(x, A) &amp; :=P\left(X_2 \in A \mid X_0=x\right) \\
&amp; =\int_{\mathbb{R}^d} P\left(X_1=x_1 \mid X_0=x\right) P\left(X_2 \in A \mid X_1=x_1, X_0=x\right) d x_1 \text { [å…¨æ¦‚ç‡å®šå¾‹] } \\
